SD.2 StructureDefinition-carin-rtpbc-ClaimResponse

title: StructureDefinition-carin-rtpbc-ClaimResponse-intro layout: default active: StructureDefinition-carin-rtpbc-ClaimResponse-intro —

This profile constrains the ClaimReponse resource so that it can serve as the RTPBC Response in the consumer real-time pharmacy benefit check process
